- Ho-ho.
- Hey, Joe, I'm on a break.

04:46.722 --> 04:49.374
- Break, huh?
- Yeah. You ever heard of one of those?

04:49.424 --> 04:51.209
No.

04:51.759 --> 04:55.345
Storm's coming. Take the load in
the morning. Stay in town tonight.

04:55.395 --> 04:59.751
